description:
Dear Listeners,

We want to help you start 2019 off right, with lots of laughter and love - which is why we’ve put together Part 2 of Unqualified’s Memorable Moments from 2018!

Wishing everyone a happy, healthy, and safe New Year!

Love, Anna, Sim, and the entire Unqualified team

  • BERT KREISCHER tells his notorious ‘Machine Story’ (1:04)
  • TOPHER GRACE shares what it was like working with Anna, some pointed advice that he gave her (11:14), and going out on the town with Wilmer Valderrama (23:45)
  • DAVID SPADE learns that Unqualified is a relationship podcast while playing Deal-Breakers (31:21)
  • KAT DENNINGS plays Swipe Left or Right (35:02)
  • BOBBY LEE gets ‘interviewed’ by Gwen Mandy on the morning show, Iced Latte Today (39:29)
  • SOPHIA BUSH discusses being single and shares her thoughts on self-love and dating (43:49)
  • MACAULAY CULKIN talks about losing his virginity (53:46)
  • ADAM RIPPON gives Anna the low-down on hooking-up at the Olympic Village (56:58)
  • JAY PHAROAH meets Karen Sarducci and impersonates Eddie Murphy (62:04)
  • BELLA THORNE and her sister, Dani, join Anna to help a caller struggling with trust issues in her relationship (69:49)
  • PETE HOLMES and Anna offer brilliant advice to a caller that’s having trouble with her boyfriend’s friends (94:00)

 

Follow us!

Anna Faris: @annakfaris

Unqualified: @unqualified
